data.description: Welcome to this beautiful wooded and level 0.72acre lot that will soon be part of a public sewer system coming Spring 2024! Utilities are at the street and the property is connected to the community water. A septic tank will need to be installed to hook-up to the public water and sewer system coming next spring. This property is peaceful and close to shops, trails, and the Little Deschutes River across the road!
